Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.64,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:20.75,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,This slave here is my recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.42,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,It's level 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.57,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's close to twenty times my level.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How much for this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:37.71,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is highly capable in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.48,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,How does 15 gold pieces sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:44.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Showing me your most expensive slave \Nknowing that I can't afford it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:48.58,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. You're sure to become \None of my best patrons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:52.36,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,so I need you to develop \Na keen eye, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:54.70,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.73,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've seen my best,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:01.46,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,let me ask you: what kind \Nof slave would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,One that's cheap and obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.91,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.12,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,a demi-human?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:12.30,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't suited for \Ncombat or manual labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I need them in battle, I'll train them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.83,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,That's an amusing response,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:19.26,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,when you don't believe in people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.26,0:01:21.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But slaves aren't people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:24.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Training one is no different \Nthan upgrading my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:28.20,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you've got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:33.50,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,These are the cheapest \Nslaves I can offer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:34.65,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,From the left...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:45.98,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,That half-raccoon is diseased \Nand has a mental disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:49.02,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a real hard time with her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:54.33,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Her previous owner loved \Nhis torture, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.60,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she'll last much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:58.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:40.74,sign_6970_33_Walking_Over_Cor,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,772)}The Slave Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.85,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.44,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.40,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,The pain will dissipate soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:07.77,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,The slave crest on her chest makes \Nit impossible for her to defy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.64,sign_5955_39_Acquired_Slave_A,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,183)}Acquired Slave A.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.93,sign_5996_40_Slave_Crest,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Slave\NCrest
