Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Party member settings"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:17.05,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,Now this girl is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty silvers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.87,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,There's one extra in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's your commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to wring it out \Nof me anyway, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.61,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly know your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:36.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I should know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.17,main,Raph,0000,0000,0000,,R-Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.69,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to your next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.77,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,So he really did choose her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.99,main,SlaveT,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting goosebumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:06.99,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.49,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.37,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... What's with the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a weapon she can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it under six silvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, draw your knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:38.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see you stab and burst this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:40.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You only hurt yourself by refusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:49.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Put more heart in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I got EXP, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:13.35,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because you set her as a\Ncompanion when forming the pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:16.93,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you didn't do that\Nwith the lady from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out, I expect you \Nto fight monsters for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.20,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you with what little money I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better help me recoup \Nyour cost, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.12,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, you're not going to \Ndie a painless death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Quit sitting around. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.67,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.21,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:50.76,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether it's our country to blame, \Nor if the kid's just been corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Three silvers left...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.35,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.56,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have all day, you little shits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:07.32,main,Merch,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, you moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.74,top,Slave,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.20,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight on an empty stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.20,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:28.76,sign_12342_95_We_don_t_serve_d,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,We don't serve demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.42,top,R,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.33,top,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.25,top,R,0000,0000,0000,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.13,top,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.04,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.55,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, it's the Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.14,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the rapist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.80,top,G,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down! He'll hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Can I order?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.85,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.75,top,W,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's a demi-human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.44,top,G,0000,0000,0000,,Why's a demi here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The cheapest lunch set you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.06,top,G,0000,0000,0000,,Someone kick her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And she'll have whatever that kid's having.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.74,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be nine coppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.41,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:01.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Because you looked like \Nyou wanted to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.00,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.55,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.89,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't taste a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.05,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.56,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.74,sign_13374_134_Skill_Tree,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Skill\NTree
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.74,sign_13374_135_Unlock_Bonus,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Mastery\NBonus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.74,sign_13374_136_Blue_Mush_Shield,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Blue Mush Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.74,sign_13374_137_ATT__0_MAG__0_P_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}ATT: 0\NMAG: 0\NP. DEF: +4\NM. DEF: +6\NDEX: 0
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.74,sign_13374_138_Fire__0_Water__0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Fire: 0\NWater: 0\NIce: 0\NWind: 0\NEarth: 0\NLightning: 0\NLight: 0\NDark: 0
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.74,sign_13374_139_Proficiency__Unl,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Proficiency\N\NUnlock Conditions\N\NUnlock Mush Shield\NBlue Mush Spores x3\NSpores of Blue Mush x2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.74,sign_13374_140_Simple_Blending_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Simple Blending Recipes 1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Blending ability, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That might come in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.62,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A hero. The shield one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You mean... One of the Four Cardinal Heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.39,flashbackitalics,RDad,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.85,flashback,RDad,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of the four legendary heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.98,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! The ones with the sword, \Nthe bow, and the spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.73,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the one with the shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:50.94,flashback,RDad,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:56.24,flashback,RDad,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero, in particular, \Ntreated us demi-humans very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.20,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'd like to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:02.83,flashback,RMom,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a good girl, I'm sure \Nyou'll meet him one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:12.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.76,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Iwatani Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.80,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Iwatani... Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.30,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.73,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's a medicine I blended.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:28.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it can cure mild colds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.69,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Good medicine tastes bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:39.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just drink it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.64,flashback,RDad,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:10.23,flashback,RMom,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to live, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:13.15,flashback,RMom,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive our selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.77,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.62,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:27.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:30.04,top,R,0000,0000,0000,,No... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.12,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:35.29,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No! Dad, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.81,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,The quality's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.10,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,Are you well versed in\N making medicines, Sir Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was my first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.56,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more profitable, \Nselling herbs or medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:02.28,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the Wave's impact,\N medicine is flying off the shelves lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.49,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd pay more for medicine than for herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.00,main,Herbist,0000,0000,0000,,In total, this is worth four silvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you have any tools \Nyou don't use anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.75,main,Kid1,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:16.46,main,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.63,main,Kid1,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.67,main,Kid1,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want one of those balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.80,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.85,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,So she wants one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can play with it {\i1}after{\i0}\Nwe're done with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.82,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.24,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.53,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, the Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to rent a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,My companion might scream at night, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}will{\i0} let us stay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.79,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course! I'll prepare a room at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:04.34,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find a way to survive before \Nthe next Wave of Catastrophe hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We can go a little \Ndeeper into the forest now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Raphtalia! Stab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.60,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... It'll bleed if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't fight, then I \Nwon't be able to look after you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A Wave that threatens the world's \Nexistence is coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:18.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get as strong \Nas I can before it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But defense is all I'm good for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I need someone to fight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it, I'll get someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.26,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to fight the Catastrophe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:34.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:54.83,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Master... I'll fight for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't throw me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.58,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:04.46,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:08.01,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to live, I have \Nno choice but to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:12.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sell us a new weapon for this amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:16.60,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get the little miss a sword, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.94,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,One on the short side would \Nbe good to start off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.73,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.69,main,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,It's a short sword made of iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:30.20,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a town or village nearby that \Nwe can travel to with our equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:36.20,top,Erh,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with your stuff, it'd have to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:39.29,sign_25674_228_The_Village_of_L,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1114,1)}The Village of Lute
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:45.17,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Around two silvers in all, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know of any spots nearby \Nwhen you can earn a lot of money quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.26,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:57.93,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The ores from that coal pit over there \Nshould fetch a decent amount, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:04.81,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the first Wave, it's become \Nhome to a bunch of dangerous monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.40,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody dares approach it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:13.20,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! I don't know what our \Nsummoned "heroes" are even doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.21,sign_13374_134_Skill_Tree,,0000,0000,0000,,Skill\NTree
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.21,sign_13374_135_Unlock_Bonus,,0000,0000,0000,,Mastery\NBonus
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.21,sign_23538_255_Rope_Shield,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Rope Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.21,sign_13374_137_ATT__0_MAG__0_P_,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}ATT: 0\NMAG: 0\NP. DEF: +15\NM. DEF: +20\NDEX: 0
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.21,sign_13374_138_Fire__0_Water__0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Fire: 0\NWater: 0\NIce: 0\NWind: 0\NEarth: 0\NLightning: 0\NLight: 0\NDark: 0
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.21,sign_13374_139_Proficiency__Unl,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Proficiency\N\NUnlock Conditions\N\NLv. 5 or Higher\NUnlock Magnet Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.21,sign_23538_259_Air_Strike_Shiel,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Air Strike Shield      Rope
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's got an exclusive effect and skill, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Rope Shield... Not exactly\Nwhat I'd call a creative name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.72,sign_23815_262_Skill_Can_be_act,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,1)}Skill\N{\fs16}Can be activated at the cost of SP.\NCan also be quick cast by shortening pronunciation or using crystals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:36.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.48,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:59.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,There are dangerous \Nmonsters here, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The moment things go south, we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.21,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.67,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,U...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:06.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:07.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:12.30,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How should I address you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Call me whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.43,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:23.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are those...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This will fetch a pretty penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, let's try over there next...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:05.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dog monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.86,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Killed all the villagers, \Neven Dad and Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,During the first Wave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.15,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why she starts \Ncrying every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the same dog that \Nkilled your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:27.50,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Take that thing out here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you fight and make me stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:39.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,we can fend off the Waves of Catastrophe \Nand prevent that tragedy from reoccurring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents won't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:47.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But we can prevent other kids \Nfrom going through what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:53.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And all I'm capable of is making \Nsure you can fight as best you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stab it with your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.45,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, so will you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:12.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Please no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry up and kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:34.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't fight, then get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.65,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy time for you to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.91,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:50.12,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be just like then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:56.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:58.76,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.77,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.20,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:29.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.35,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:55.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, even with the shield's power,\N the wound still hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:59.81,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever die! Please don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.69,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.65,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,She chose my name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You attack, and I defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That way, neither of us will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:11.79,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:15.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving once I feed \Nthis monster to my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.09,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.55,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get off already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,A bit longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:04.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The ore made us a lot of money, \Nso you can eat all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:05.16,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:08.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.07,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:10.91,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:16.15,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.17,0:23:20.57,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Let's survive, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.57,0:23:22.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.55,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here. A kids' lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,isn't complete without this.
